00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:30.795
Today we are going to worship the Devi,

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:37.956
we call her Amba, and by many other
names.

00:00:43.320 --> 00:00:48.474
She is the last, we should say, the
''residual power''

00:00:49.680 --> 00:00:52.513
When she has done everything

00:00:53.480 --> 00:00:57.393
she becomes the Kundalini

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:02.676
and settles in the triangular bone of yours.

00:01:04.720 --> 00:01:07.359
This is the Mooladhara Chakra.

00:01:09.800 --> 00:01:17.388
But actually she is expressed more on the
left side,

00:01:19.440 --> 00:01:25.310
because that time she is purely the Amba.

00:01:30.720 --> 00:01:37.114
This left side is a very, very important

00:01:38.040 --> 00:01:41.510
thing for all the human beings.

00:01:43.160 --> 00:01:46.118
lf you have no left side,

00:01:46.480 --> 00:01:50.109
you cannot balance yourself, to begin
with.

00:01:51.280 --> 00:02:00.518
And it is said that she gives you a real
personality

00:02:03.920 --> 00:02:05.478
of a Sahaja Yogi.

00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:18.515
That is, your left side, if it is weak,

00:02:20.480 --> 00:02:23.870
then you have to worship her;

00:02:24.960 --> 00:02:31.752
and request her that ''Please enrich our
left side''.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:36.470
By enriching your left side,

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:40.710
what she does, she is a comforter,

00:02:41.160 --> 00:02:44.470
So, what does she give you? First of all,

00:02:44.960 --> 00:02:47.155
she makes you rest.

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:50.755
lt is said that she makes you rest.

00:02:51.200 --> 00:02:55.990
That is, she makes you sleep.

00:02:57.160 --> 00:02:59.993
lf you are too much thinking about future

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:05.758
and you are so much indulging into the
futuristic planning,

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:08.637
you have some problems;

00:03:10.120 --> 00:03:12.395
but the best thing is if you can sleep,

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:17.195
then it is a great comfort,

00:03:17.640 --> 00:03:20.871
it is a very great comfort to you that you
can sleep

00:03:21.400 --> 00:03:24.915
and that you can take some rest.

00:03:26.080 --> 00:03:28.196
Without her you cannot sleep:

00:03:28.640 --> 00:03:32.189
absence of her, you cannot sleep.

00:03:35.520 --> 00:03:41.470
So sleeping is a very important function of
the body,

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:45.470
which is brought forth by the left side.

00:03:46.760 --> 00:03:48.910
That's why we worship her,

00:03:49.320 --> 00:03:53.632
because she should give us rest.

00:03:54.360 --> 00:03:56.635
She's the one who gives you peace;

00:03:58.720 --> 00:04:07.879
She's the one who gives you also
illusions,

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:11.634
called as Bhranti.

00:04:13.520 --> 00:04:18.036
She gives you all the artistic talents,

00:04:19.360 --> 00:04:21.316
she protects you.

00:04:22.560 --> 00:04:30.592
But this part that she is creating illusions
for you

00:04:32.480 --> 00:04:35.074
that's very, very important.

00:04:36.160 --> 00:04:42.633
Because those people who are against
Divine,

00:04:45.080 --> 00:04:51.553
who are trying to be away from the reality,

00:04:52.680 --> 00:04:55.638
she creates illusions for them.

00:04:56.720 --> 00:05:00.315
So she separates you from those people,

00:05:01.560 --> 00:05:03.516
while you know the reality

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:11.873
and all such people who are troubling or

00:05:12.840 --> 00:05:16.150
trying to destroy her work

00:05:17.360 --> 00:05:22.150
She is the one who creates illusions.

00:05:22.680 --> 00:05:27.913
She is the one who resides as the
Kundalini.

00:05:29.080 --> 00:05:37.317
So we can say that part of her is the
Kundalini,

00:05:38.920 --> 00:05:44.631
but another part that she has

00:05:46.040 --> 00:05:49.350
is the one which resides in the left side.

00:05:51.760 --> 00:06:02.671
Now there are seven levels

00:06:06.120 --> 00:06:09.669
which she resides.

00:06:11.760 --> 00:06:17.153
Once you start enjoying her on the first
level,

00:06:18.320 --> 00:06:22.791
then She has all these qualities described
to you.

00:06:24.760 --> 00:06:26.591
That She is peace,

00:06:27.040 --> 00:06:32.353
She is the one who gives you love,

00:06:32.760 --> 00:06:40.075
She is the one who creates all the
beautiful things for you.

00:06:43.800 --> 00:06:45.870
She is the Mother.

00:06:46.360 --> 00:06:51.354
And what She expects you is to enjoy her
protection,

00:06:51.800 --> 00:07:00.549
enjoy her love and be always under her
complete protection.

00:07:03.920 --> 00:07:09.756
So this is a very important part of her
work.

00:07:10.800 --> 00:07:14.509
And the second one is that She is the
Kundalini.

00:07:16.320 --> 00:07:19.278
So She also acts on seven levels.

00:07:21.200 --> 00:07:26.433
Seven levels She moves, we can say
horizontally,

00:07:29.400 --> 00:07:33.837
and seven levels she moves upward.

00:07:35.760 --> 00:07:39.389
And all these seven levels, on both of the
sides.

00:07:40.760 --> 00:07:43.354
She does tremendous work for us.

00:07:46.400 --> 00:07:51.235
How she protects us through these seven
levels, is like this,

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:55.198
that even if you start going towards the
left side,

00:07:57.000 --> 00:08:00.959
there are seven Deities

00:08:01.440 --> 00:08:05.433
which try to throw you back into normalcy.

00:08:06.440 --> 00:08:10.433
There are Shankini, Dhankini, these are
the names.

00:08:12.440 --> 00:08:19.471
And by that you try to come to normal
conditions.

00:08:20.600 --> 00:08:23.876
Now for example, many psychosomatic
diseases

00:08:24.440 --> 00:08:29.798
which come to us, like cancer and so
many others;

00:08:30.760 --> 00:08:38.952
psychosomatic means it is physical as
well as it is emotional.

00:08:40.920 --> 00:08:43.878
So these psychosomatic troubles

00:08:44.280 --> 00:08:46.874
start coming from the left side.

00:08:48.840 --> 00:08:51.832
Sometimes you are too much on the right
side,

00:08:53.160 --> 00:08:56.277
then suddenly you are thrown to the left
side, suddenly.

00:08:57.120 --> 00:09:01.557
And then the movement like a pendulum,
you can go any far.

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:05.436
But there are seven powers on the
left-hand side

00:09:05.880 --> 00:09:10.237
which protect you from getting into these
diseases;

00:09:11.240 --> 00:09:19.397
also reducing their intensity.

00:09:23.080 --> 00:09:28.837
So at one time, she is the one who is
peace giving,

00:09:29.840 --> 00:09:36.029
she is the one who looks after you and
protects you,

00:09:37.040 --> 00:09:40.828
and she is the one who saves you

00:09:41.160 --> 00:09:44.516
from psychosomatic diseases.

00:09:46.200 --> 00:09:50.637
ls a very powerful entity.

00:09:52.720 --> 00:09:56.315
lf she was not there l don't know what
would have happened.

00:09:58.320 --> 00:10:01.995
So we should worship her within
ourselves.

00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:06.829
We should respect her, and understand
her;

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:09.638
she is your Mother.

00:10:11.720 --> 00:10:14.518
As Kundalini she is your particular Mother.

00:10:16.160 --> 00:10:20.358
She is the one, Amba,

00:10:22.160 --> 00:10:24.754
who gives you your second birth.

00:10:27.040 --> 00:10:35.709
And as the left side goddess

00:10:36.960 --> 00:10:44.753
she gives you a very good support in your
ascent.

00:10:45.920 --> 00:10:48.593
A very good support in your ascent.

00:10:48.920 --> 00:10:52.390
Without her you could not balance
yourself.

00:10:54.440 --> 00:10:57.000
This goes too far sometimes

00:10:57.440 --> 00:11:01.479
when people are too much on the right
side.

00:11:03.600 --> 00:11:06.910
Then they get diseases which are very
funny.

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:11.312
They can get heart-attack, they can get
paralysis.

00:11:12.440 --> 00:11:16.228
They also get the right side completely
paralysed.

00:11:16.640 --> 00:11:19.950
They can't walk, they can't lift themselves.

00:11:20.840 --> 00:11:23.479
This is too much of right side movement.

00:11:24.640 --> 00:11:34.390
So then she is the one who makes you
feel bad about it.

00:11:36.400 --> 00:11:40.951
She is the one who suggests that you
give up your right side

00:11:42.760 --> 00:11:45.877
and take more to the left side.

00:11:47.920 --> 00:11:50.195
So that doesn't mean that right side,

00:11:50.560 --> 00:11:54.314
if it is cured by the left side, it is very good.

00:11:54.680 --> 00:11:58.878
For example, a person who is very
arrogant, egotistical,

00:12:00.120 --> 00:12:05.911
such a man may become absolutely
docile,

00:12:07.160 --> 00:12:08.832
and people might think he is cured.

00:12:09.160 --> 00:12:13.278
No. He is on the left side.

00:12:13.680 --> 00:12:19.198
Though he has become docile, still he is
not normal.

00:12:20.280 --> 00:12:25.798
Still he is very much wrong because he is
on the left side.

00:12:26.920 --> 00:12:32.119
On the left side one starts getting many
diseases

00:12:32.360 --> 00:12:37.036
like schizophrenia, on the upper level of
this group.

00:12:38.320 --> 00:12:43.030
This side these same seven centres

00:12:43.600 --> 00:12:46.672
act to give you very serious troubles.

00:12:47.640 --> 00:12:52.475
One of them is that people become
schizophrenic.

00:12:53.520 --> 00:12:58.548
lt can be cured; it can be cured if you can

00:12:59.080 --> 00:13:02.993
move that person to the centre.

00:13:04.000 --> 00:13:06.753
And by Kundalini awakening you can do
it.

00:13:07.160 --> 00:13:11.438
Then people also become mad, lunatic.

00:13:12.520 --> 00:13:16.069
But all the troubles of the right side
disappear.

00:13:18.000 --> 00:13:20.468
Such people who have moved to the left
side

00:13:20.920 --> 00:13:22.911
won't have liver problems.

00:13:25.480 --> 00:13:26.993
They might have enlarged liver,

00:13:27.320 --> 00:13:29.675
but over-active liver they won't have.

00:13:30.120 --> 00:13:34.989
They won't have other symptoms like
asthma, hear-attack.

00:13:37.160 --> 00:13:38.957
They cannot have heart attack.

00:13:39.320 --> 00:13:41.072
They'll give heart attacks to others

00:13:41.520 --> 00:13:43.988
but they themselves don't get heart
attacks.

00:13:45.360 --> 00:13:47.157
So this

00:13:48.880 --> 00:13:52.953
sudden movement of your attention into
the left side

00:13:54.080 --> 00:13:58.039
is all the time guarded by these seven
entities,

00:13:58.520 --> 00:14:01.159
or goddesses,who look after you.

00:14:01.280 --> 00:14:03.510
But still if you go on with it:

00:14:05.680 --> 00:14:08.148
