anyone

00:14:24.520 --> 00:14:28.479
whom they have captured and whom they
are looking after

00:14:29.040 --> 00:14:33.636
as a kind of a possession for others.

00:14:34.760 --> 00:14:38.594
This is tantrika, they people possess

00:14:39.120 --> 00:14:43.193
the spirits of these dead people

00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:46.797
and use them to entice you.

00:14:48.160 --> 00:14:55.396
So when you start getting into the left side
by any means,

00:14:56.480 --> 00:14:58.994
you can get it by worrying too much,

00:14:59.360 --> 00:15:03.876
you can get it by feeling very sorry for
something,

00:15:04.920 --> 00:15:07.514
or crying, weeping, anything,

00:15:08.840 --> 00:15:14.437
then your right side problems disappear.

00:15:15.560 --> 00:15:17.278
That is why you do it.

00:15:18.560 --> 00:15:20.198
But it goes too far.

00:15:20.600 --> 00:15:24.070
The right side problems are, if they are
cured,

00:15:24.560 --> 00:15:27.870
you get the left side problems which are
much more dangerous.

