they just follow it.

00:42:53.440 --> 00:42:55.749
They don't see what they have achieved,

00:42:56.120 --> 00:42:59.954
what have they got, what is the use,
nothing.

00:43:00.920 --> 00:43:03.878
Even when you buy something you want
to find out

00:43:05.800 --> 00:43:07.552
what is the quality;

00:43:07.720 --> 00:43:10.359
the person who has purchased, how is he
using,

00:43:10.720 --> 00:43:12.039
everything you want to find out.

00:43:12.360 --> 00:43:15.796
But when it comes to following the
fashion, nobody thinks about it.

00:43:16.240 --> 00:43:20.916
And the fashion is created to be fool
people, also, l think so.

00:43:22.120 --> 00:43:30.994
lt is something very funny creation of the
evil force,

00:43:32.040 --> 00:43:34.998
so that human beings should be
destroyed.

00:43:38.040 --> 00:43:41.271
lt is, they say, the designers.

00:43:41.760 --> 00:43:44.513
l say it is nothing, designers or anything,

00:43:44.840 --> 00:43:49.311
but is their aggressive force, their
negative force

00:43:49.680 --> 00:43:51.636
which works on you;

00:43:51.840 --> 00:43:54.957
and who saves you is the Mother on the
left side.

00:43:56.080 --> 00:44:00.790
She has got seven curtains. Seven
boundaries

00:44:01.240 --> 00:44:03.276
she doesn't want you to cross over.

00:44:03.720 --> 00:44:06.553
But human beings say: ''Why not? Why
not me?

00:44:07.000 --> 00:44:09.992
lf they have gone to hell, l'll also go to
hell''.

00:44:10.400 --> 00:44:16.236
All right. That's been made already for
you, so go ahead.

00:44:16.600 --> 00:44:19.433
So that's why she creates the Bhranti;

00:44:19.840 --> 00:44:25.597
because some people have to go out, out
of this circulation,

00:44:25.920 --> 00:44:29.230
out of this evolution process. Let them go
out.

00:44:29.600 --> 00:44:33.070
This is the Last Judgement. All right, that's
how you'll be judged,

00:44:33.600 --> 00:44:36.478
by your own stupidity you'll be judged.

00:44:39.400 --> 00:44:43.996
l have told so many Sahaja Yogis
something small,

00:44:45.200 --> 00:44:47.350
that you must put some oil in the nights

00:44:47.640 --> 00:44:49.312
and the morning time you wash.

00:44:49.640 --> 00:44:51.358
But they don't do it.

00:44:52.680 --> 00:44:57.037
But by doing that what happens is that
you soothe yourself,

00:44:58.240 --> 00:44:59.832
you sleep well.

00:45:00.800 --> 00:45:04.395
Oiling is a very good thing. We need it all
of us,

00:45:04.760 --> 00:45:07.320
especially in this cold weather, we need it.

00:45:07.720 --> 00:45:09.039
But they won't put it.

00:45:09.560 --> 00:45:11.551
They'll neglect themselves.

00:45:12.040 --> 00:45:14.190
Because they think they're Sahaja Yogis

00:45:14.520 --> 00:45:16.511
they are protected, Mother can oil them.

00:45:16.960 --> 00:45:20.953
lt's not so. You have to look after yourself.

00:45:21.400 --> 00:45:26.428
As far as the body is concerned, the mind
is concerned,

00:45:41.360 --> 00:45:43.920
you are responsible for your body.

00:45:44.240 --> 00:45:48.074
With Sahaja Yoga you will understand
what's wrong with you,

00:45:49.320 --> 00:45:50.799
what you are doing wrong.

00:45:51.160 --> 00:45:54.232
l mean l tell you some things which are
very important,

00:45:54.640 --> 00:45:59.589
but to you they may not be, but you
should try that.

00:46:00.960 --> 00:46:04.430
As it is you are Realised Souls, your spirit
is there,

00:46:04.760 --> 00:46:06.432
you can feel the vibrations,

00:46:06.760 --> 00:46:09.399
and you can understand what's wrong
with the person.

00:46:10.640 --> 00:46:15.031
Mostly what l have seen, now it is much
less,

00:46:15.440 --> 00:46:20.468
that people only inform me always about
people who are possessed.

00:46:20.880 --> 00:46:23.553
''Mother, such and such person is
possessed''.

00:46:23.880 --> 00:46:26.189
''Mother this person has got this
possession''.

00:46:26.520 --> 00:46:30.559
l said, ''But, throw them out!'' That's all!

00:46:34.480 --> 00:46:36.835
Why do you want me to bother about
them?

00:46:37.360 --> 00:46:39.191
Just throw them out!

00:46:39.680 --> 00:46:42.433
Then after going out of Sahaja Yoga they
will realise,

00:46:42.720 --> 00:46:45.314
then they will say ''Mother we don't want
to go out of Sahaja Yoga''.

00:46:45.600 --> 00:46:48.478
Why? Because they know that now

00:46:48.840 --> 00:46:52.833
they are completely away

00:46:54.120 --> 00:46:57.954
from reality and from safety.

00:46:59.200 --> 00:47:00.758
So they want to come back.

00:47:02.160 --> 00:47:04.879
Those who can come back can come
back.

00:47:05.280 --> 00:47:08.397
But those who should not come back
should never come back.

00:47:09.480 --> 00:47:13.871
Because they are so mad that they'll
create a fashion of madness,

00:47:14.920 --> 00:47:17.309
and people can get influenced by that.

00:47:17.720 --> 00:47:22.430
So to get influenced by others is not a
sign of a Sahaja Yogi.

00:47:23.560 --> 00:47:25.676
He can influence others,

00:47:26.040 --> 00:47:31.876
but how does he get influenced by others
but for Sahaja Yoga?

00:47:32.240 --> 00:47:35.596
Sahaja Yoga is the discriminating power.

00:47:35.920 --> 00:47:38.275
And who has given you this is the
Kundalini.

00:47:38.600 --> 00:47:41.160
So this Kundalini which is your mother,

00:47:41.480 --> 00:47:45.792
the one which is now in your triangular
bone, also

00:47:46.280 --> 00:47:50.796
gives you all the qualities and all the
beauties of your being.

00:47:51.200 --> 00:47:53.794
Of course l have told you so many things
about Kundalini

00:47:54.120 --> 00:47:55.678
that l need not tell you.

00:47:56.320 --> 00:48:00.711
But she also can correct the left side.

00:48:01.880 --> 00:48:04.519
Some people have a habit

00:48:04.880 --> 00:48:09.351
of all the time crying and weeping over. l
don't know.

00:48:10.720 --> 00:48:13.678
Every time you meet them they are in
tears:

00:48:14.080 --> 00:48:15.559
''And what has happened?''

00:48:15.920 --> 00:48:19.708
''Mother this has happened, that has
happened'' and all that.

00:48:20.000 --> 00:48:22.150
They write letters after letters to me,

00:48:22.480 --> 00:48:25.040
telling about their woes, their troubles and
this and that.

00:48:25.440 --> 00:48:27.396
Baba you are Sahaja Yogis now.

00:48:27.840 --> 00:48:35.633
Now you are in the Garden of Eden, you
are in the heavens.

00:48:36.160 --> 00:48:39.277
And why are they thinking about all the
hellish things

00:48:39.560 --> 00:48:42.074
which are not important? Why?

00:48:43.440 --> 00:48:47.592
Because you haven't got your individuality
either.

00:49:12.360 --> 00:49:17.673
Now as Sahaja Yogis you have to develop
your discrimination

00:49:18.240 --> 00:49:21.789
of understanding what others are.

00:49:22.360 --> 00:49:24.590
Also about yourself.

00:49:25.080 --> 00:49:29.551
Why do you hanker after things? Try to
understand.

00:49:30.040 --> 00:49:32.076
What is so great about it?

00:49:33.520 --> 00:49:35.272
Why do you want to do it?

00:49:36.680 --> 00:49:38.477
Question yourself.

00:49:39.560 --> 00:49:41.278
ls it some possession?

00:49:44.680 --> 00:49:46.591
ls it some fashion?

00:49:47.400 --> 00:49:51.234
Or is it your individual feeling?

00:49:54.680 --> 00:49:57.194
So, l'm trying to tell you

00:49:57.560 --> 00:50:01.880
that this left side of yours is so protective,

00:50:01.880 --> 00:50:02.118
that this left side of yours is so protective,

00:50:03.560 --> 00:50:06.313
at the same time

00:50:06.800 --> 00:50:09.951
if you are very aggressive about your left
side

00:50:11.200 --> 00:50:14.954
you are thrown from one to another to
another to another into hell.

00:50:17.320 --> 00:50:19.470
And then you suffer.

00:50:20.880 --> 00:50:27.069
So you must understand, your wisdom
should be there,

00:50:27.400 --> 00:50:31.632
which you can develop very much with
the help of the left side.

00:50:32.120 --> 00:50:35.078
Wisdom can be very well developed.

00:50:37.120 --> 00:50:40.829
Now there's somebody, say a Sahaja
Yogi, so called,

00:50:41.360 --> 00:50:47.435
and he is absolutely aggressive,
money-oriented, deceitful

00:50:48.560 --> 00:50:50.949
and you get into his trap.

00:50:54.840 --> 00:50:58.150
ln Hindi we call it Chakkar, Chakkar.

00:50:59.240 --> 00:51:04.598
And once you get involved into that you
go on drifting;

00:51:05.840 --> 00:51:11.153
still your left side will protect, up to a point.

00:51:12.320 --> 00:51:17.189
But if you are too much of it, it throws you
''Get out, get out''.

00:51:19.400 --> 00:51:22.233
Now the time has come for all of us to
understand

00:51:22.720 --> 00:51:24.278
that you are all Sahaja Yogis

00:51:24.600 --> 00:51:27.273
and you have a very big responsibility,

00:51:28.200 --> 00:51:31.431
very, very big responsibility that you
should do

00:51:33.000 --> 00:51:37.039
what your enlightened conscience tells
you.

00:51:38.080 --> 00:51:43.313
Take to your enlightenment and live under
that light,

00:51:43.720 --> 00:51:46.518
and don't jump in the darkness.

00:51:47.480 --> 00:51:50.472
And by that you will also understand

00:51:50.880 --> 00:51:53.792
who is the right person and who is not the
right person.

00:51:56.440 --> 00:51:59.955
Even in Sahaja Yoga this negativity can
work,

00:52:00.400 --> 00:52:02.595
it works.

00:52:03.760 --> 00:52:06.194
And one should not get involved

00:52:06.640 --> 00:52:10.235
into any negative thoughts of others,

00:52:10.640 --> 00:52:12.995
or negative doing of others.

00:52:16.320 --> 00:52:19.517
lt's a warning today l wanted to give you
all,

00:52:19.920 --> 00:52:28.669
because you people are very much there,
to enjoy.

00:52:31.600 --> 00:52:34.672
Look after your attention, where does it
go.

00:52:37.000 --> 00:52:39.070
There is so many beautiful things,

00:52:39.400 --> 00:52:41.118
see the flowers, so beautiful!.

00:52:41.480 --> 00:52:43.550
See this thing they have made so
beautifully.

00:52:43.840 --> 00:52:46.149
lt makes my heart jump with joy;

00:52:47.560 --> 00:52:49.551
while some people don't even notice.

00:52:51.160 --> 00:52:52.639
The other day l asked somebody,

00:52:52.920 --> 00:52:55.753
''Who had made that flower
arrangement?'' ''Which flower?''

00:52:56.280 --> 00:52:59.829
l said ''The one that was there'' ''Which
one?''

00:53:00.760 --> 00:53:04.196
So l told the names of the flowers. ''We
never saw''

00:53:04.600 --> 00:53:06.511
Where were you looking,

00:53:08.200 --> 00:53:10.395
that you couldn't see the flowers?!

00:53:10.880 --> 00:53:13.269
Because your eyes are so stupid

00:53:13.560 --> 00:53:15.391
that they cannot see the beauty.

00:53:15.720 --> 00:53:20.669
They are engulfed with all kinds of
negative things.

00:53:21.600 --> 00:53:25.434
So the goddess has to kill all the
rakshasas.

00:53:27.640 --> 00:53:31.428
l don't know how many she has killed,
and again they are back.

00:53:32.560 --> 00:53:34.994
And again people are being trapped.

00:53:37.040 --> 00:53:38.792
This is going on.

00:53:40.200 --> 00:53:44.193
So these rakshasas are there and you
have to pin-point them.

00:53:44.680 --> 00:53:48.275
And tell people ''Where are you going?
He's a rakshasa.

00:53:49.520 --> 00:53:53.991
What he has done, what has he
achieved?''

00:53:54.440 --> 00:53:56.795
Now you should talk like that;

00:54:00.120 --> 00:54:02.190
openly.

00:54:02.720 --> 00:54:05.029
So you can save many people

00:54:05.480 --> 00:54:07.596
who are going to these rakshasas,

00:54:07.880 --> 00:54:13.159
who are coming in such clothes that you
cannot make them out.

00:54:14.440 --> 00:54:18.991
They will be destroyed, one by one,

00:54:19.480 --> 00:54:22.438
but when they are in the heart of so many
people

00:54:22.720 --> 00:54:24.472
how can you destroy them?

00:54:26.760 --> 00:54:29.069
So it is for you people to tell them

00:54:29.600 --> 00:54:32.114
what these rakshasas are doing.

00:54:33.240 --> 00:54:35.196
l know their tricks,

00:54:35.640 --> 00:54:40.634
but the worst part is that the human
beings fall into their tricks.

00:54:41.840 --> 00:54:46.755
So you have to be very
self-understanding.

00:54:47.960 --> 00:54:49.916
Ask always the question ''Why?

00:54:50.360 --> 00:54:52.635
Why am l attracted to this?

00:54:53.120 --> 00:54:55.111
What is the gain?''

00:54:55.560 --> 00:54:57.835
Ask yourself this question.

00:55:00.560 --> 00:55:02.073
You'll find

00:55:02.440 --> 00:55:05.750
that after coming to Sahaja Yoga you
have gained so much.

00:55:06.760 --> 00:55:09.832
So now, why have this false idea?

00:55:10.120 --> 00:55:14.033
why go after false things, negative things?

00:55:16.040 --> 00:55:18.076
That's what Sahaja Yogis have to do,

00:55:18.520 --> 00:55:21.910
because not that they're responsible for
others,

00:55:22.200 --> 00:55:24.919
they are responsible for themselves also.

00:55:27.000 --> 00:55:30.037
Now the sweetest thing said about her is

00:55:30.400 --> 00:55:33.676
that she gives you Shraddha.

00:55:35.680 --> 00:55:38.877
Shraddha we can translate it as faith.

00:55:40.920 --> 00:55:46.472
To have faith, rightly not wrongly.

00:55:47.720 --> 00:55:52.111
People take full advantage if you have
wrong faiths.

00:55:53.960 --> 00:55:57.999
But faith is very important, that she gives
also.

00:56:01.080 --> 00:56:03.913
And that's very joy-giving.

00:56:04.440 --> 00:56:07.159
The faith is very joy-giving.

00:56:08.320 --> 00:56:13.519
But when the incarnations lived, nobody
believed in them.

00:56:14.680 --> 00:56:16.750
They had no faith in them.

00:56:17.280 --> 00:56:19.316
Christ, they crucified,

00:56:19.840 --> 00:56:22.752
nobody stood up to say, ''Why are you
crucifying him?''

00:56:25.000 --> 00:56:32.554
All of them; nobody could have that faith
to stand up.

00:56:33.960 --> 00:56:36.349
They may fight for their own country,

00:56:36.640 --> 00:56:39.313
they may fight for their religion or own
nonsense,

00:56:39.600 --> 00:56:44.276
but, ''That a man, this man, is really the
Truth,

00:56:44.800 --> 00:56:49.669
he is the one who is an incarnation'',
nobody will say it.

00:56:53.160 --> 00:56:55.196
So yesterday l was stunned

00:56:56.360 --> 00:57:00.239
to see the drama they have shown.

00:57:00.760 --> 00:57:03.115
l mean, l couldn't face myself, l should
say.

00:57:03.640 --> 00:57:05.631
Though it's the Truth, of course, l agree.

00:57:05.920 --> 00:57:07.797
But l couldn't face myself.

00:57:08.160 --> 00:57:11.914
l am too humble to accept such a thing,

00:57:12.440 --> 00:57:17.719
and it's very ingenious, it's very great to
create such a drama

00:57:20.200 --> 00:57:23.715
and of all the things. At first l had said that

00:57:24.120 --> 00:57:27.954
the English have such a sense of drama,

00:57:28.280 --> 00:57:30.669
they had people like Shakespeare and all
that,

00:57:31.000 --> 00:57:34.197
and the way they were producing drama l
couldn't understand.

00:57:34.480 --> 00:57:37.392
But this one was the last word on
perfection.

00:57:37.800 --> 00:57:40.997
So much so that l couldn't say a word
about it.

00:57:41.520 --> 00:57:43.158
l was just stunned.

00:57:44.400 --> 00:57:47.358
The Truth that they have propounded.

00:57:48.600 --> 00:57:55.039
But in my lifetime you will have no doubts,

00:57:55.560 --> 00:57:58.120
if you have some sense in you.

00:57:59.480 --> 00:58:02.552
Because so many miracles are taking
place.

00:58:03.040 --> 00:58:04.996
Today only somebody told me:

00:58:05.480 --> 00:58:08.756
''Somebody had cancer,

00:58:12.280 --> 00:58:13.918
ulcer and all kinds of things,

00:58:14.360 --> 00:58:16.749
and after Sahaja Yoga

00:58:17.120 --> 00:58:19.680
she went to the hospital and she had
nothing''.

00:58:20.960 --> 00:58:24.077
All such miracles are taking place. Leave
alone.

00:58:24.520 --> 00:58:28.229
Also there are never have happened like
this

00:58:28.640 --> 00:58:32.633
that there are photographs of mine

00:58:34.560 --> 00:58:38.155
where you see, is remarkable.

00:58:38.720 --> 00:58:41.234
Even the scientists are surprised at it,

00:58:41.600 --> 00:58:43.795
how these photographs are coming.

00:58:45.840 --> 00:58:50.311
Actually there was Shri Ganesha standing
behind it actually.

00:58:50.600 --> 00:58:53.398
Only in one camera it came.

00:58:53.840 --> 00:58:57.469
lt is just for you people to have faith.

00:58:57.960 --> 00:59:01.111
Because when the person is not there,

00:59:01.360 --> 00:59:04.636
like Christ is no more, now everybody's
going to church.

00:59:05.160 --> 00:59:08.118
Shri Rama is not there so they are all
singing his praise.

00:59:08.600 --> 00:59:11.876
Shri Krishna is not there so they are ''Hari
Rama, Hari Krishna''.

00:59:14.680 --> 00:59:18.355
So when there is Sakshat, when that is
before you,

00:59:18.640 --> 00:59:20.835
you don't accept.

00:59:21.800 --> 00:59:25.554
Because perhaps you don't believe you
can deserve it, perhaps.

00:59:25.880 --> 00:59:29.031
Or may be it is, l don't know,

00:59:29.320 --> 00:59:31.550
human beings it is very difficult to
understand them.

00:59:31.840 --> 00:59:34.308
When you are standing before them they
don't believe.

00:59:34.640 --> 00:59:36.870
When you are no more, then they will
believe.

00:59:37.240 --> 00:59:40.073
lt is a very funny thing, isn't it?

00:59:40.400 --> 00:59:42.994
All through out if you see the history of
spirituality

00:59:43.280 --> 00:59:45.350
this has been going on.

00:59:47.480 --> 00:59:50.790
Gyanadeva showed some miracles, still

00:59:52.800 --> 00:59:55.837
only the wise, only the sensible

00:59:56.200 --> 00:59:58.668
could understand and believe it.

00:59:59.200 --> 01:00:01.960
And there is so few that as a result

01:00:01.960 --> 01:00:02.597
And there is so few that as a result

01:00:03.040 --> 01:00:06.032
such people are crucified, killed or done
anything.

01:00:08.080 --> 01:00:10.799
They have tried that with me,

01:00:11.160 --> 01:00:16.029
but you know in this life l have come in all
Forms,

01:00:16.400 --> 01:00:18.789
and nobody can destroy me:

01:00:19.240 --> 01:00:23.233
Unless and until l want to finish myself, no
one can.

01:00:25.120 --> 01:00:30.069
The powers are of love, affection,
compassion,

01:00:30.480 --> 01:00:33.790
but also there's a power

01:00:35.000 --> 01:00:38.834
which completely corrects other people.

01:00:41.040 --> 01:00:47.752
So to you people not to have faith in
Sahaja Yoga

01:00:48.320 --> 01:00:50.993
shows complete blankness,

01:00:51.520 --> 01:00:53.272
you have seen the photographs,

01:00:53.680 --> 01:00:56.638
you have seen everything, you have
known the miracles,

01:00:56.960 --> 01:01:00.555
it has happened to you. You have the
experience of Sahaja Yoga.

01:01:00.960 --> 01:01:03.599
Despite that your faith is so weak.

01:01:05.160 --> 01:01:07.469
She's the one who gives you faith,

01:01:07.840 --> 01:01:11.276
so you have to praise her, you have to fall
at her feet,

01:01:11.600 --> 01:01:16.799
you have to worship her and ask her ''Oh
Mother, give us that faith''.

01:01:17.840 --> 01:01:19.956
And with this faith you'll be amazed,

01:01:20.440 --> 01:01:22.715
any person who has this kind of a faith,

01:01:23.080 --> 01:01:25.833
he tells me ''Mother, please, do this''

01:01:26.320 --> 01:01:28.675
lt happens. lt just happens.

01:01:29.800 --> 01:01:36.035
Such right they have got to ask for
anything. lt works out.

01:01:36.440 --> 01:01:40.035
But first your faith should be solid.

01:01:40.480 --> 01:01:42.471
Faith should be real.

01:01:42.840 --> 01:01:47.356
lf it is real and if it is deep,

01:01:48.480 --> 01:01:50.436
you can achieve whatever you want.

01:01:50.880 --> 01:01:53.110
Not wrong, but good things.

01:01:54.280 --> 01:01:57.636
And so try to develop that faith

01:01:58.120 --> 01:02:03.035
and as a faith gives you such joy and
happiness,

01:02:03.400 --> 01:02:06.597
you get committed, you get involved,

01:02:07.000 --> 01:02:09.275
and you don't want to get out of it.

01:02:10.560 --> 01:02:17.955
So the greatest thing is the blessing of the
