01:02:19.360 --> 01:02:21.351
Faith which is pure,

01:02:21.880 --> 01:02:27.557
faith can be translated as, we can say,
Vishwas

01:02:27.960 --> 01:02:31.839
but not. Faith is Shraddha.

01:02:33.120 --> 01:02:37.272
Shraddha means something that is within;

01:02:38.880 --> 01:02:41.075
which has no doubts,

01:02:42.680 --> 01:02:45.717
which has no doing as such, it is just
there.

01:02:46.320 --> 01:02:48.595
